}}{{TIDTOC|embedded}} ==Overview== "MPB-800U Rev:UD" is silkscreened on the main board in the FCC photos. "081R-WMD370AN00 R05" and "MP060113400038" is on a label on the Mini PCI card in the FCC photos. U-MEDIA appears to be the OEM.
The default SSID is per the FCC manual. It may not be accurate..
3rd party Linux firmware is not supported on the Ubicom processor.
